Classes in twcore.core used by twcore.bots
BotAction
          The main bot utility class, your bot's best and easiest method of performing actions in the arena, getting information on players, scheduling tasks to be performed, and much more.
BotSettings
          Reads, stores, and allows access to the settings in a bot's configuration file.
EventRequester
          Used to request which events will be sent to a bot.
OperatorList
          Stores the access list as read from the server-based files moderate.txt, smod.txt, and sysop.txt, and the bot core config files owner.cfg, outsider.cfg, and highmod.cfg.
SubspaceBot
          Basic abstract class that all Subspace bot classes must extend.
